              | With UMS we are combining resources to continue to deliver amazing co-working spaces throughout the Southeast like that of <a class="green-text" href="http://soco-work.com/">SOCO</a>. Great startups benefit from creative and collaborative environments for professionals to spark innovation amongst one another and The Unmatched Style team is a proven, local innovator. We canâ€™t wait to get going!
          
          .col-sm-4
            h2 Address
            p(style="font-size:16px; margin-top:3px") The Iron Yard - Columbia <br>
              | 823 Gervais Street<br>
              | Columbia, SC 29201
            a(href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/823+Gervais+St/@34.000225,-81.039344,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m2!3m1!1s0x88f8bb2c4b95de31:0x625ccd3cc2dcccce" class="btn")
              | Directions              

      .horizontal-section.gray-light-bg#programs
        .container
            .row
              .col-md-6
                img.photo(src="/images/locations/columbia/columbia-academy.jpg")
